Task: 09
Title: Domain streaming extension
Phase: 3
Route: full
Slice: Streaming Synthesis + Timeouts
Dependencies: 08
Scope: Extend ChatModelPort with a stream() method signature and define the ChatStreamEvent discriminated union (token, done, error) in the domain port. This is a cross-phase modification of src/domain/ports/chat-model-port.ts (originally created in Task 02) — justified because streaming is a Phase 3 capability and the port was intentionally defined with only complete() in Phase 1 to keep the initial system simple. The ChatStreamEvent type is distinct from FusionStreamEvent: it represents raw LLM token events from the port, which the use case translates into FusionStreamEvents.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-3 (partial — stream() signature)
NFRs: NFR-1
Gate Criteria: Phase 3 Gate 1 (stream() signature available for application and adapter)
Files:
  - src/domain/ports/chat-model-port.ts (MODIFY) — Add ChatStreamEvent discriminated union (token, done, error) and stream(request: ChatRequest): AsyncIterable<ChatStreamEvent> method to ChatModelPort interface
